/ 歌手值得撐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:45:48.000Z","msg":"022. 漫長<br />\nRubberBand"},{"pid":"05cc8968979c2f0f7a26dea85379459cbcce088d","tid":2283894,"uid":66049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:47:04.000Z","msg":"Tell me what 柒you say"},{"pid":"2da1312e62072d04c73b3398cbd91f48ef45656b","tid":2283894,"uid":184592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:47:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a03fbe554bf17ff6c0d9bf75f028ba6d960f363","tid":2283894,"uid":184592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:48:29.000Z","msg":"<em>連日來連登仔力推《人話》</em><br />\n唔覺嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb56a56eef512710257622dbae82316988be1049","tid":2283894,"uid":72994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:51:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"af6322b9a2af76c154ef9fc99e5ff0afa2229adc","tid":2283894,"uid":184592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f27586a92dbce8beb11c3be9637af85d09031fc","tid":2283894,"uid":5499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:39:03.000Z","msg":"方便大家，人話係28號<br />\n<br />\n不如樓主提議埋仲有邊首歌/ 歌手值得撐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:51:59.000Z","msg":"《RTHK十大中文金曲》開始投票喇，11月15日截止，投完幫手推!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2278130\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2278130</a><br />\n<br />\n呢度有詳細討論"},{"pid":"66bad1612bf0fbcc6ac17c11f45e0553f5fd3f4f","tid":2283894,"uid":266015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:53:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4ed6fd83593322f217b73d3ed06c72b370452662","tid":2283894,"uid":170812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:55:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9bda3133ad8b439e68d7884d941a4fb634c55ce3","tid":2283894,"uid":184592,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"6f27586a92dbce8beb11c3be9637af85d09031fc","tid":2283894,"uid":5499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:39:03.000Z","msg":"方便大家，人話係28號<br />\n<br />\n不如樓主提議埋仲有邊首歌/ 歌手值得撐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T03:04:21.000Z","msg":"只屬參考：<a href=\"https://lih.kg/aFhMEpV\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aFhMEpV</a><br />\n<br />\n最好係大家都認真聽下先投，唔好鳩投<br />\n鳩投而唔支持本地音樂冇意思"},{"pid":"72dac8b2243b5450b120dd211533ad1adfbe6ae0","tid":2283894,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T03:12:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201113/6ZXMOFI6FNEHDNCSNX3EYJCKDU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201113%2F6ZXMOFI6FNEHDNCSNX3EYJCKDU%2F&d=K%2BViKRLCts5CIle5BUc%2BymCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=69443144\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201113%2F6ZXMOFI6FNEHDNCSNX3EYJCKDU%2F&h=1ef4e3ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201113/6ZXMOFI6FNEHDNCSNX3EYJCKDU/</a><br />\n<br />\n【投票機制】樂迷結果佔七成<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/uBdag17glagw7T_iMEf1Vi1aT74=/950x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/AG5QJKQ6GZHSDGPULVAS6AWQG4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FuBdag17glagw7T_iMEf1Vi1aT74%3D%2F950x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FAG5QJKQ6GZHSDGPULVAS6AWQG4.jpg&h=b64151bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港台《第43屆十大中文金曲頒獎典禮》將於明年1月16日錄播，網上投票已在進行中。在港台頒獎禮一眾獎項中，金曲獎、國語歌曲獎、新人獎、男歌手獎、女歌手獎、樂隊/組合獎及至尊金曲獎等，評分準則是樂迷投票佔70%；而專業評選團則佔30%，因此投票對結果是十分之重要。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：港台頒獎禮網上投票 手足齊撐同路歌手  方皓玟《人話》爭至尊金曲 延續黃色音樂圈<br />\n<br />\n至於入圍準則，只要歌曲、歌手、樂隊或組合曾登上中文歌曲龍虎榜三甲位置，皆自動成為候選歌曲及男、女歌手獎等人選。國語歌曲獎則只要曾上中文歌曲龍虎榜便可加入候選。"},{"pid":"de725ac47dfeeac9ce6b0d7b75012a1cc2088a4a","tid":2283894,"uid":89823,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"6f27586a92dbce8beb11c3be9637af85d09031fc","tid":2283894,"uid":5499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:39:03.000Z","msg":"方便大家，人話係28號<br />\n<br />\n不如樓主提議埋仲有邊首歌/ 歌手值得撐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T03:31:41.000Z","msg":"陳健安 馮允謙 許廷鏗<br />\n方皓玟 Serrini 鄧小巧<br />\nKOLOR RubberBand ToNick Yellow!野佬"},{"pid":"9260b94fefa2e4b7443c6324d52f3e738a50c81d","tid":2283894,"uid":24853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T03:51:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6fa1c56f920045564e8095078f2f0a8225f10d35","tid":2283894,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64890a83bb98c9151a9bd0494fe9b5385a72e019","tid":2283894,"uid":50526,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:17:49.000Z","msg":"投票link<br />\n<a href=\"http://rthk.hk/goldsong2020\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frthk.hk%2Fgoldsong2020&d=K%2BViKRLCts5CIle5BUc%2BymCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=7998dac8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://rthk.hk/goldsong2020</a><br />\n要SMS 驗證"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T04:06:47.000Z","msg":"人話 係 28號"},{"pid":"8af6ad4489d27e6abc398a5ad63dd0c848f07707","tid":2283894,"uid":23098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T04:11:52.000Z","msg":"幻愛 小塵埃<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e815d9d113a6b4e160c78ac921bcaa8a43d760d","tid":2283894,"uid":48143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T04:14:14.000Z","msg":"撐！！！！！<br />\n加油呀小明"},{"pid":"c84cdc785dbc1e9e831b7315f7383e7a80a59afe","tid":2283894,"uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime